“The Short Meter” is a culmination of decades of ASA’s R&D experience. Crafted with extra-durable materials, and coated with an ASA-patented “+Mag” coating, the boots are more durable, and provide greater comfort than other manufacturers’ boots. Manufactured by ASA Tech.

Includes:

- High comfort material.
- “+Mag” patented coating for higher durability.
- A mini-jet engine at the heels to allow for bursts of
magnificent speed.
